<page>
    <shortlink>transform gettingstarted</shortlink>
    <topic>Getting Started with Alpha TransForm</topic>
    <description>Are you ready to master TransForm? Our three part Alpha TransForm Tutorial will walk you through the basics of creating your first form in Alpha TransForm.</description>
    <groups>
        <group>
            <title>TransForm Tutorial - Part 1</title>
            <sections>
                <section>
                    <description>
                        <p>*[[Start Tutorial Part 1]]*</p>
                        <p>In part 1 of the TransForm Tutorial, we walk you through the process of creating, filling, and submitting your first form in Alpha TransForm.</p>
                        <p>*[bold:What You'll Learn:]*</p>
                    </description>
                    <list bullet="true">
                        <item>
                            <name>Creating an Account</name>
                        </item>
                        <item>
                            <name>Using the Designer</name>
                        </item>
                        <item>
                            <name>Creating new forms using the Quickstart Editor</name>
                        </item>
                        <item>
                            <name>Uploading forms to the TransForm cloud</name>
                        </item>
                    </list>
                    <figure>
                        <link>/images/transformCentralHome.png</link>
                    </figure>
                </section>
            </sections>
        </group>
        <group>
            <title>TransForm Tutorial - Part 2</title>
            <sections>
                <section>
                    <description>
                        <p>*[[Start Tutorial Part 2]]*</p>
                        <p>In part 2 of the TransForm Tutorial, we teach you how to download forms to your mobile device using the Alpha TransForm app. Then, we show you how to fill out and submit the form to the TransForm cloud.</p>
                        <p>*[bold:What You'll Learn:]*</p>
                    </description>
                    <list bullet="true">
                        <item>
                            <name>Installing the Alpha TransForm App</name>
                        </item>
                        <item>
                            <name>Downloading form types</name>
                        </item>
                        <item>
                            <name>Creating a new form from a form type</name>
                        </item>
                        <item>
                            <name>Filling out and saving forms, including capturing photo, location, and signature information</name>
                        </item>
                        <item>
                            <name>Uploading forms to the TransForm cloud</name>
                        </item>
                    </list>
                    <figure>
                        <link>/images/app6.png</link>
                    </figure>
                </section>
            </sections>
        </group>
        <group>
            <title>TransForm Tutorial - Part 3</title>
            <sections>
                <section>
                    <description>
                        <p>*[[Start Tutorial Part 3]]*</p>
                        <p>In part 3 of our TransForm tutorial, we take you back to TransForm Central where we show you where to go to view form data that has been uploaded to the TransForm cloud as well as how to add and manage users in your TransForm account.</p>
                        <p>*[bold:What You'll Learn:]*</p>
                    </description>
                    <list bullet="true">
                        <item>
                            <name>Viewing uploaded forms in the Management Console</name>
                        </item>
                        <item>
                            <name>Adding users to your TransForm account</name>
                        </item>
                        <item>
                            <name>Modifying user permissions in your TransForm account</name>
                        </item>
                    </list>
                    <figure>
                        <link>/images/manage1.png</link>
                    </figure>
                    <figure>
                        <link>/images/manageUserRoles.png</link>
                    </figure>
                </section>
            </sections>
        </group>
    </groups>
